    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in incredible shape and looking just as fresh as the day it rolled off the lot. If you're looking for something that\u2019s been pampered and is ready for a new home, this is the one! Super smooth ride, spotless interior\u2014it\u2019s basically perfect. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
