    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional example in showroom condition, meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior paint is flawless, protected by a high-end ceramic coating that delivers a deep, glass-like finish with absolutely zero rock chips or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, the carpets are pristine under factory mats, and it has never been smoked in. Mechanically, this vehicle is perfect, backed by a complete, chronological service history from an authorized dealer. It has just undergone a major inspection, including all fluid changes and a fresh set of high-performance tires. Every feature, from the infotainment to the smallest toggle switch, operates exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. This is a collector-grade vehicle for a buyer who demands perfection.",
