    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready for your dream ride? This car is absolutely stunning and in total mint condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken incredible care of it, and there's not a scratch or a smudge to be found. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh new-car smell. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Come swing by and see it for yourself\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
