    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade R32 GT-R featuring the legendary RB26DETT twin-turbocharged inline-six. This specimen retains its original ceramic turbos and factory-spec intercooler, delivering linear power through the ATTESA E-TS torque-split AWD system. The chassis is exceptional, with the Super HICAS four-wheel steering system fully recalibrated and a multi-link suspension that remains tight and responsive. The undercarriage is free of oxidation, and the engine bay maintains all original heat shielding and zinc-plated hardware. Inside, the cockpit is flawless, lacking the common dashboard bubbling or bolster fatigue. A rare survivor that delivers a visceral, mechanically pure driving experience.",
